{
  "stem": "11000.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they marched us to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was a special train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were deported.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were sent to a camp up north called Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Westerbork was a-- I would say, a proper word would be a transient camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "All individual, all prisoners that were shipped to Germany or to Eastern Europe had to go through Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's where they were registered, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And from Westerbork, the trains left every Tuesday to the east.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the unique thing about Westerbork was they had a huge hospital.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And here again, if you arrived in Westerbork and you were sick, you were not assigned on a transport.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "First, you were sent to the hospital so make sure that you are well, to present the image that you are not good to us if you cannot produce.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So first, let's cure you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then we'll send you to the gas chambers and to be gassed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Of course, we all didn't know that at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But that was Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have difficulty with the time element.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember, we arrived there on November 11, 1942.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's when we were deported.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when we arrived, I remember the commander of the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His name was Obersturmbannfuhrer Gemmeker.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was a German, like you see the cartoonists make him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was 17 years old at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was in good physical condition.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was assigned as-- in the garbage collection group, which meant I got a little wheelbarrow and a barrel.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I had to go to the barracks and empty out the small barrels into the big barrel.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then I had to wheel them to the pile outside the camp where the garbage was.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it didn't bother me.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
